# Deployment

This repo does NOT use GitHub Actions workflows. Do not create, modify, or reference `.github/workflows/` files.

## How to deploy

Deploy to GitHub Pages manually using:

```bash
npm run deploy
```

This runs `astro build`, adds `.nojekyll`, and pushes the `dist/` folder to the `gh-pages` branch via the `gh-pages` npm package.

## After pushing to main

Pushing to `main` does NOT auto-deploy. Always run `npm run deploy` after pushing changes that should go live.
